OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering daytime showers should fade
OL,7,Fthrough the evening giving way to a
OL,8,Fdry but cloudy night. This blanket of
OL,9,Fcloud will allow for temperatures to
OL,10,Fremain mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy at first, with a few
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning.
OL,14,FHowever, this will clear and skies
OL,15,Fwill brighten through the afternoon
OL,16,Fwith some warm sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
